text: Aleksandr Martynov or Alexandr Martynov (born 1 January 1981Moldova chronology, Worldstatesmen.org) is a Transnistrian politician. He was the Prime Minister of Transnistria from 17 December 2016 until 30 May 2022 under the presidency of Vadim Krasnoselsky. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Transnistria
title: Aleksandr Martynov (Transnistrian politician)
